{"tid":2463431,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Heat Project 重制版 Heat Reborn 公測 （3）","createTime":"2021-03-26T16:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T16:34:43.000Z","uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f5b2ffb28bdc9eee8c3ba261cd8a789d73787140","tid":2463431,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:33:21.000Z","msg":"【Steam平台不刪檔公測現已開始！】<br />\n大家的回憶 回來了！《HEAT REBORN 火線特戰隊》帶來 遊戲平衡完全重新調整、A.I.電腦玩家、隊內語音、多張經典（故宮、旺角）地圖和 4K 武器高清重製、高達６０人同時的多人對戰、以及 全新「競技比賽配對」系統等等！<br />\n<br />\n由本地小型業餘獨立遊戲開發團隊，以全新引擎重新製作呈現經典MMORPGFPS遊戲！<br />\n現在於 Steam 平台，按「要求存取權」立即加入《HEAT REBORN 火線特戰隊》 BETA！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://heatreborn.com/zh?feed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheatreborn.com%2Fzh%3Ffeed&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=41bc53b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://heatreborn.com/zh?feed</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVJJr2n9932g2CKbsixNrW1XUWnt2UTknokAXk1rh4oBx?filename=cvbxsNe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvbxsNe.png&h=d123bc9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTrQTqweohGfpA43XjXnfZmTtiguc6sPSjvdqFCjfgFKf?filename=kNd4iTV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNd4iTV.png&h=8e4f3f71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"848235398208cc23ef03d436bd9556f5337a9d1b","tid":2463431,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbaPiTtK5iHs6RgG3pPToYGSceiZuP5aNvRonRz3bVKhh?filename=3kJWUsP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kJWUsP.png&h=5e4a6eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【地伏盃#1 報名即將截止 &mdash; 反應熱烈、剩餘少量名額！】<br />\n感謝各位的支持，首個《HEAT REBORN》社群主辦比賽報名反應熱烈～🎉<br />\n除了所有出席比賽的參賽者均可獲得「參賽福利」，我們同時也將獎品數量再「加碼覆蓋至正選及後備隊員（共 8 名）！」<br />\n<br />\n報名即將於3月28日23:59分截止，名額有限，先到先得！<br />\n８強賽事開始將會全程於Twitch及YouTube直播，不論閣下抱持火氣還是學習態度均能滿足！<br />\n<br />\n比賽詳情請參閱 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/devilscuphr01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fdevilscuphr01&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=04fb2098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/devilscuphr01</a><br />\n或可到CGA比賽平台 <a href=\"https://vs.cga.gg/tournament/devilscupHR01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvs.cga.gg%2Ftournament%2FdevilscupHR01&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b78741cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vs.cga.gg/tournament/devilscupHR01</a><br />\n<br />\n[1] 個別玩家（１－５人）也可以報名，系統將會幫助各位隨機組隊（系統會自動識別人數不足的隊伍）<br />\n[2] 滿人隊伍將擁有參賽優先權，個別玩家報名將會被置於滿人隊伍後處理<br />\n[3] 有關比賽或相關問題，敬請聯繫主辦單位 Devils Gaming 查詢，謝謝"}]}